  <brief_title>Immunogenicity of Influenza Vaccines in HIV-infected Persons in Thailand</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Controlled Trial to Compare the Immunogenicity of Intramuscular Versus Intradermal Trivalent Inactivated Split Virion Influenza Vaccine in HIV-infected Men Who Have Sex With Men in Bangkok, Thailand</official_title>
  <sponsors>
